    public class AppletBoot
extends java.applet.Applet
implements java.lang.Runnable
    This class handles JADE start-up and shut-down when running JADE as an Applet. The split-container mode is used.
    Requires the LEAP add-on
    Author:
    Giovanni Caire - TILAB
